      <title>Truck Overhaul and New Ghosts!</title>
      <pubDate>Sunday, 12 June 2022</pubDate>
      <description>
	&lt;p&gt;Happy holidays, everyone! KineticGames has just released the new Truck Overhaul update!&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;The changelog contains three new ghosts called the Deogen, Moroi, and the Thaye.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;The Truck has been given a major facelift.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;A higher quantity of utilities are allowed to be brought with you into the mission.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Happy Hunting!&lt;/p&gt;
      </description>
