      <title>Christmas Update is live!</title>
      <pubDate>Friday, 10 Dec 2021</pubDate>
      <description>
	&lt;p&gt;Happy holidays, everyone! KineticGames has just released the new Christmas update!&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;The changelog contains new additions, including a new ghost called The Mimic as well as items which are called "Cursed Posessions".&lt;/p&gt; 
	&lt;p&gt;(Please keep an eye out for new P.E.T. updates which should roll out very soon).&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;Be sure to visit the official Phasmophobia Discord for more information.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;From all of us at TritiumGamingStudios, stay safe and take care!&lt;/p&gt;
      </description>
